OL,3,CNottingham Attacks: Police officers
OL,4,Cunder investigation
OL,6,FThree Leicestershire Police officers
OL,7,Fare under investigation over how they
OL,8,Fdealt with alleged assaults by Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane the month before he killed
OL,10,Fthree people in Nottingham.
OL,12,FTwo constables and a sergeant have
OL,13,Fbeen told they are being investigated
OL,14,Fover how inquiries were progressed,
OL,15,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,16,FConduct said.
OL,18,FIt is claimed that Calocane assaulted
OL,19,Ftwo colleagues at an industrial estate
OL,20,Fin Kegworth, Leicester, in May last
OL,21,Fyear.
