OL,6,FThe following month, he went on to
OL,7,Fkill students Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,8,FO'Malley-Kumar, along with caretaker
OL,9,FIan Coates, in a knife rampage in
OL,10,FNottingham.
OL,12,FSanjoy Kumar, father of Grace O'Malley-
OL,13,FKumar has told ITV News: "If officers
OL,14,Fat Leicestershire had done their jobs
OL,15,Fthe course of Calocanes life would
OL,16,Fhave changed and even if his course
OL,17,Fhad changed a few degrees our beloved
OL,18,Fand brave daughter would still be
OL,19,Fhere, I am sure of that.
