OL,6,F"We were updated with regards to the
OL,7,Fthree separate investigations that are
OL,8,Ftaking place with Nottingham Police
OL,9,FForce, Leicestershire Police Force and
OL,10,Falso into the conduct of the Chief
OL,11,FConstable of Nottingham Police Force.
OL,13,F"At this time we are unable to give
OL,14,Fdetailed comment, however suffice to
OL,15,Fsay we remain deeply concerned at the
OL,16,Fsheer scale of failings and poor
OL,17,Fdecision making that has taken place
OL,18,Facross both forces.
