OL,6,F"We have been forced to endure yet
OL,7,Fmore trauma in the amount of
OL,8,Finformation, actions and time we have
OL,9,Fbeen forced into in ensuring we
OL,10,Fprovide all of our detailed evidence.
OL,12,F"We have to trust that the IOPC will
OL,13,Faddress every single matter raised and
OL,14,Ftake appropriate and accountable
OL,15,Faction to all concerned. As soon as
OL,16,Fthe outcome of each investigation is
OL,17,Fmade public we will be able to comment
OL,18,Fin much greater detail"
